1. Understand what data do I have
    a. Sales Target:
        - Month of Order Data: "Apr-18, May-18"
        - Category: str, {Furniture, Clothing, Electronics}
        - Target: float 
    
    b. Order Details
    What is the difference between Amount and Quantity?
        - Order ID: B-00000
        - Amount: float 
        - Profit: float
        - Quantity: int 
        - Category: str 
        - Sub-Category: str 

    c. List of Orders
        - Order ID: B-00000
        - Order Date: Date
        - CustomerName: Str
        - State: str
        - City: str 

